{"url": "https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/527756.The_Man_Without_Qualities", "title": "The Man Without Qualities", "titleComplete": "The Man Without Qualities", "description": "Set in Vienna on the eve of World War I, this great novel of ideas tells the story of Ulrich, ex-soldier and scientist, seducer and skeptic, who finds himself drafted into the grandiose plans for the 70th jubilee of the Emperor Franz Josef. This new translation\u2014published in two elegant volumes\u2014is the first to present Musil's complete text, including material that remained unpublished during his lifetime.", "imageUrl": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1647816500i/527756.jpg", "genres": ["Germany", "Novels", "Literature", "Classics", "Historical Fiction", "Literary Fiction", "20th Century", "German Literature", "Fiction", "Philosophy"], "asin": "0330349422", "isbn": "0330349422", "isbn13": "9780330349420", "publisher": "Alfred A. Knopf", "series": ["The Man Without Qualities"], "author": ["\u041c\u0430\u0440\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0438\u0442\u0430 \u0418\u0432\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u0430", "Robert Musil", "Burton Pike", "Solomon Apt", "Sophie Wilkins"], "publishDate": 788947200000, "characters": ["Ulrich", "Dr. Paul Arnheim", "Franz Joseph I of Austria"], "places": ["Vienna", "Austro-Hungarian Empire"], "ratingHistogram": [174, 325, 959, 1833, 3413], "ratingsCount": 6704, "reviewsCount": 471, "numPages": 1774, "language": "English", "awards": [{"name": "Prix du Meilleur Livre \u00c9tranger", "awardedAt": -378662400000, "category": "Novel", "hasWon": null}, {"name": "\u041d\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u043d\u0430 \u043d\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u0430 \u201e\u0425\u0440\u0438\u0441\u0442\u043e \u0413. \u0414\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u201c", "awardedAt": 1230796800000, "category": "\u041f\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043e\u0434\u043d\u0430 \u0445\u0443\u0434\u043e\u0436\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0435\u043d\u0430 \u043b\u0438\u